- gh not installed: Provide install instructions
- Not authenticated: Prompt to run gh auth login
- Network error: Retry with exponential backoff
- Repo exists: Ask to overwrite or use different name

### GitHub Pages Limits

- Site size: Max 1 GB
- Per-file: Max 100 MiB (warn at 50 MiB)
- Bandwidth: 100 GB/month soft limit

### Exit Criteria

